Package uniol.apt.generator

Classes for systematic generation of PetriNets and TransitionSystems.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NetGenerator
    Interface for generators of Petri nets of a given size.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPetriNetIterableWrapper
    This class makes it easier to apply some "generator function" to each petri net in an Iterable which generates more petri nets.
    GeneratorUtils
    Some common utility functions that various generators need.

Package uniol.apt.generator Description

Classes for systematic generation of PetriNets and TransitionSystems. For example, CycleGenerator creates a PetriNet where tokens are moved from one place to another in a cyclic fashion.
